ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectPassport and Other Travel Document Services Fees Regulations
PrecisPASSPORT AND OTHER TRAVEL DOCUMENT SERVICES FEES REGULATIONS in order to offer a 10-year ePassport for the lowest possible fee while ensuring it generates sufficient revenues to deliver Passport Canada's mandate regarding passport security and client service over a 10-year business cycle.
